OL,3,CCommunities with high flood risk 'face
OL,4,Cservice cuts' as defence costs rise
OL,6,FCommunities at the highest risk of
OL,7,Fflooding face cuts to key frontline
OL,8,Fservices due to a sharp rise in the
OL,9,Fcost of local defences, councils have
OL,10,Fwarned.
OL,12,FThere are calls for the Government to
OL,13,Foverhaul the way bodies which oversee
OL,14,Fflood alleviation in the lowest-lying
OL,15,Fareas are funded as current
OL,16,Farrangements risk penalising nearly a
OL,17,Fmillion households who already pay to
OL,18,Fmaintain flood defences through
OL,19,Fcouncil tax.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
