OL,3,CCommunities with high flood risk 'face
OL,4,Cservice cuts' as defence costs rise
OL,6,FThere is a legal requirement for
OL,7,Fcouncils to pay the levy charges once
OL,8,Fagreed, but there are Government
OL,9,Frestrictions on annual council tax
OL,10,Frises.
OL,12,FTherefore, councils are unable to
OL,13,Fincrease bills to cover drainage
OL,14,Fboards' extra costs, meaning less
OL,15,Fmoney is available to pay for services
OL,16,Fand invest in housing and economic
OL,17,Fgrowth.
