OL,3,CCommunities with high flood risk 'face
OL,4,Cservice cuts' as defence costs rise
OL,6,FTaxpayers in affected areas face an
OL,7,Foverall flood protection bill this
OL,8,Fyear of #50 million, paid primarily
OL,9,Fthrough council tax and landowner
OL,10,Flevies.
OL,12,FThe three districts facing the biggest
OL,13,Flevy increases this year are all in
OL,14,FLincolnshire.
OL,16,FEast Lindsay will see the levy rise by
OL,17,F35% to #1.37 million, followed by
OL,18,FBoston and South Holland with
OL,19,Fincreases of #700,000 and #600,000
OL,20,Frespectively.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
