OL,3,CCommunities with high flood risk 'face
OL,4,Cservice cuts' as defence costs rise
OL,6,FFor Boston Borough Council, the
OL,7,Fdrainage levy makes up 22% of its
OL,8,F#12.76 million annual net budget.
OL,10,FThe authority collects #4.33 million
OL,11,Fin council tax, of which 61% goes on
OL,12,Fthe drainage levy.
OL,14,FThe DCN said that while overall high
OL,15,Fenergy costs are driving financial
OL,16,Fpressures, standing charges for energy
OL,17,Fregardless of how much is used are
OL,18,Fparticularly costly for pumping
OL,19,Fstations that are used infrequently,
OL,20,Fbut are vital at times of heavy rain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
