OL,3,CCommunities with high flood risk 'face
OL,4,Cservice cuts' as defence costs rise
OL,6,FSam Chapman-Allen, DCN chairman and
OL,7,FConservative leader of Breckland
OL,8,FCouncil, said: "It is only by properly
OL,9,Ffunding flood prevention that defences
OL,10,Fcan be maintained over vast swathes of
OL,11,Fthe country and we avoid catastrophic
OL,12,Fflooding threatening life and
OL,13,Flivelihood.
