OL,6,F"Internal Drainage Authorities have
OL,7,Flittle option but to pass their higher
OL,8,Fcosts onto councils ` and in response
OL,9,Fcouncils have no choice but to further
OL,10,Fcut back on the local services which
OL,11,Fare vital for supporting local
OL,12,Fcommunities and growing local
OL,13,Feconomies.
OL,15,F"The areas affected are the homes and
OL,16,Fworkplaces of millions of people, and
OL,17,Fare vital for in achieving our
OL,18,Fnational priorities ` growing our
OL,19,Feconomy, building new homes and
OL,20,Fenhancing food security.
